Package required:


nfs-kernel-server - support for NFS kernel server
nfs-common	- NFS support files common to client and server

wsdd		- Python Web Services Discovery Daemon, Windows Net Browsing               
samba		- SMB/CIFS file, print, and login server for Unix
smbclient	- command-line SMB/CIFS clients for Unix

rsync		- fast, versatile, remote (and local) file-copying tool
minidlna	- lightweight DLNA/UPnP-AV server targeted at embedded systems
openssh-server	- secure shell (SSH) server, for secure access from remote machines

lua5.1		- Simple, extensible, embeddable programming language
liblua5.1-0	- Shared library for the Lua interpreter version 5.1                

mtd-utils	- Memory Technology Device Utilities
debian-keyring	- GnuPG keys of Debian Developers and Maintainers
lvm2		- Linux Logical Volume Manager
curl		- command line tool for transferring data with URL syntax
gnupg2		- GNU privacy guard - a free PGP replacement (dummy transitional package) 
cpufrequtils	- utilities to deal with the cpufreq Linux kernel feature
usbutils	- Linux USB utilities
discover	- hardware identification system

x11-apps	- X applications 
xauth		- X authentication utility



Packages to remove (broken on ARM soft FP or cause huge increase in initrd):

plymouth		- boot animation, logger and I/O multiplexer
openjdk-17-jre-headless - OpenJDK Java runtime, using Hotspot Zero (headless)
